## Example 4: Inventory Management

Track product inventory across warehouses:

```typescript
const inventoryCSV = `
product_id,product_name,warehouse,quantity,reorder_level,unit_cost,value
P001,"Laptop Pro",WH1,45,20,899.99,40499.55
P001,"Laptop Pro",WH2,12,20,899.99,10799.88
P002,"Monitor 27",WH1,120,50,349.99,41998.80
P002,"Monitor 27",WH2,75,50,349.99,26249.25
