## Example 5: Error Handling and Data Cleaning

Handle malformed data gracefully:

```typescript
const messyCSV = `
id,name,email,signup_date,email_verified
1,John Doe,john@example.com,2024-01-01,true
2,Jane Smith,jane@example.com,2024-01-02
